-- Mvelaphanda May Abstain from Avusa Vote on Universal Print, Times Reports
-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 2010-10-13T05:43:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/mvelaphanda-may-abstain-from-avusa-shareholers-vote-on-uhc-times-reports.html
Mvelaphanda Group Ltd., which owns
25.5 percent of South African media company Avusa Ltd., may
abstain from voting on the company’s bid to buy Universal Print
Group and Hirt & Carter after trying to block the transaction,
the Times reported, citing an Mvelaphanda official that it
didn’t identify.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  